Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.88,0:22:37.16,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}探して見つけ出すために
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.14,0:22:42.30,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}遅く起きた朝でも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.38,0:22:48.96,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}毎日目を覚ますんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:51.56,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}It's not too late
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.66,0:22:55.13,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}We say hello
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.30,0:23:01.46,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}ちょっとでも笑って
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.56,0:23:07.65,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}いつだってこの世界は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.75,0:23:14.31,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}あなたが必要だから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.40,0:23:16.49,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}It's not too late
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.61,0:23:19.40,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}We say hello
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.53,0:23:23.48,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}We say hello
